dct_title_s: Topographic map of Fredericksburg and vicinity, Virginia, showing battlefields
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Map shows fortifications, Lee's headquarters, transmission line, railroads, roads, and some streets. "Surveyed in 1931." "Advanced sheet subject to correction." Map is a preliminary versio. The battlefields location is not included.
